Is that you,
Mr. Solverson? Yeah.

35:02.200 --> 35:03.679
We've been trying to...

35:03.760 --> 35:05.876
I mean, all night
we've been calling,

35:05.960 --> 35:07.997
and the operator didn't
know where you were...

35:08.080 --> 35:10.390
What happened?
Well, it's...

35:11.200 --> 35:12.873
She's fine...

35:12.960 --> 35:14.678
Just had a...

35:15.680 --> 35:17.512
Well, she fell,
is all.

35:17.920 --> 35:20.116
Something about
the pills they gave her.

35:20.920 --> 35:22.479
What do you mean,
she fell?

35:22.560 --> 35:25.598
Where's Molly?
She's here. At home.

35:26.320 --> 35:27.515
