35:41.880 --> 35:44.998
(MUMBLES) But the doctor...
He says your missus is fine.

35:45.840 --> 35:49.993
Just needs rest and then to come
in next week for some more tests.

35:51.720 --> 35:53.870
She's sleeping currently.

35:53.960 --> 35:57.316
I told her I'd sit up with
Molly until you got home.

35:59.240 --> 36:01.311
Okay, well, uh,

36:01.400 --> 36:03.437
I got a suspect
in custody.

36:03.520 --> 36:06.160
On my way back from
Sioux Falls, so, uh...

36:06.800 --> 36:10.759
Tell Betsy I'll be home
soon as I can. Okeydoke.

36:10.840 --> 36:12.194
And, Noreen?

36:12.840 --> 36:15.116
Thank you.
You betcha.

