37:03.800 --> 37:08.237
And so, great empires fall
and are forgotten.

37:20.440 --> 37:23.592
You're thinking,
why Tripoli?

37:24.920 --> 37:30.040
Well, Tripoli, not to be
confused with Levantine Tripoli

37:30.440 --> 37:32.317
in the country
of Lebanon,

37:32.400 --> 37:35.995
was founded in Libya in the
seventh century by the Phoenicians.

37:37.120 --> 37:38.952
Then was conquered
by the Romans.

37:41.000 --> 37:44.356
And then by the Spanish
and then by the Turks.

37:46.440 --> 37:48.431
You see where I'm going.

37:50.680 --> 37:52.353
I need a face man.

37:54.040 --> 37:55.951
His details are inside.

37:57.360 --> 38:00.671
I'm assuming you want
more than just a skin peel.

38:01.520 --> 38:03.796
Something structural...

38:04.600 --> 38:06.318
A whole new man.

38:07.040 --> 38:10.078
Like the phoenix,
rising from the ashes.

38:12.200 --> 38:13.998
What'll you do then,
I wonder.

38:15.720 --> 38:19.076
Join a new empire?

38:20.520 --> 38:22.511
Maybe start
one of my own.

38:24.640 --> 38:26.517
So that it, too,

38:26.600 --> 38:29.718
may one day collapse
and fall into the sea.

38:32.200 --> 38:35.272
Do I take it you'll try to get
revenge on Kansas City?

38:35.360 --> 38:37.271
Apprehend those
responsible?

38:38.080 --> 38:40.913
"Cause you can bet Kansas City
will be heavily guarded.

38:41.360 --> 38:42.873
Not apprehend.

38:43.320 --> 38:44.390
Dead.

38:44.920 --> 38:47.116
Don't care
"heavily guarded."â€

