(LAUGHS)

42:14.160 --> 42:16.037
Uh, anyway, settle in.

42:16.120 --> 42:19.397
Dale from HR's gonna come by
with a few forms for you to fill out,

42:19.480 --> 42:21.710
health insurance, 401Kk...

42:21.800 --> 42:23.871
And then, uh,
get to work.

42:23.960 --> 42:27.112
Quarterly projections and revenue
