(CHUCKLES) Yeah. He'll
show up again, I'm sure...

44:53.680 --> 44:55.273
Like it or not.

44:58.200 --> 44:59.998
You okay, hon?
Yeah, sure.

45:01.080 --> 45:02.434
(SIGHS)
It's just a cramp.

