45:19.840 --> 45:23.117
Well, we're sitting
here together.

45:23.520 --> 45:24.954
That's what matters.

45:27.000 --> 45:28.354
A man once said,

45:29.320 --> 45:31.516
"You'll know the angels
when they come,

45:33.040 --> 45:35.759
cause they'll have
the faces of your children."

45:36.360 --> 45:39.000
Anyway. (LAUGHS)
Um...

45:39.480 --> 45:41.630
Just happy to
see you is all, Bet.

45:48.480 --> 45:51.836
So, Dad, I fed your cats
while you were in the hospital.

45:52.560 --> 45:54.836
And they're grateful,
